      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TARAWI BRUMBY (3) was below best last time at Wentworth Park (30.12) in a Grade 5, finishing a 4.5 lengths fourth. Yet to taste defeat in two runs from this draw. Expected to go close. FORTY'S BOY (2) improved his time on first attempt here at the trip with a 2 length second in 29.81 latest. Rates a leading chance if runs up to latest. HAYDEN'S FANCY (7) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Has finished in the placings two on end now, the latest when second (29.92) at this track. Has a good record here including three wins. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Hard to beat again. ANNIE'S RUPEE (8) had won two starts on end leading into the last outing when strongly fancied but could only manage seventh (21.46) at this track. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong.",
